<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6c275120-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s1967"><num value="1967">§ 1967.</num><heading> United States release from liability</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The United States shall not be liable for any debts, defaults, acts, or omissions of the Foundation nor shall the full faith and credit of the United States extend to any obligation of the Foundation.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id6c275121-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/449/s117">Pub. L. 109–449, § 117</ref>, formerly <ref href="/us/pl/116/224/tI/s117">Pub. L. 116–224, title I, § 117</ref>, <date date="2020-12-18">Dec. 18, 2020</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/134/1080">134 Stat. 1080</ref>; renumbered <ref href="/us/pl/109/449/s117">Pub. L. 109–449, § 117</ref>, by <ref href="/us/pl/119/65/s3/a">Pub. L. 119–65, § 3(a)</ref>, <date date="2025-12-26">Dec. 26, 2025</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/139/1987">139 Stat. 1987</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
